content: mmarfinetz: Merged two significant PRs this month, with #2784 introducing a new arbitrage plugin with example character (+121,270/-9,888 lines) and #2869 improving gas price optimization and volume calculations (+4,187/-3,144 lines). These contributions represent substantial feature development work, with the arbitrage plugin PR being particularly extensive. The PRs took an average of 34 hours to merge, suggesting efficient review processes despite their complexity.
